name: MesonWrapGAM
summary: MesonWrapGAM SDK is a light weight SDK, and the single access point, to all the S2S bidding demand.
description:
MesonWrapGAM is an Mobile In-App, S2S Header Bidding wrapper that can be seamlessly 
   integrated into your app with a light weight SDK. You can add as many demand sources 
   on the server side to maximize the competition for an impression in an auction without 
   any hassles.
